Interface IconMultiStateFormatting

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HSSFIconMultiStateFormatting, XSSFIconMultiStateFormatting 

    public interface IconMultiStateFormatting
    High level representation for the Icon / Multi-State Formatting component of Conditional Formatting settings(Conditional Configuration设置的Icon / Multi-State Configuration组件的高级表示)
